1. Make changes to source files
2. Test locally across multiple browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
3. Test responsiveness on various device sizes
4. Validate HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
5. Check accessibility with automated tools
6. Optimize images using `tools/png_to_webp.py` if adding new images
7. Update Service Worker cache version if assets changed
8. Test PWA functionality (offline mode, caching)
9. Deploy via Git (GitHub Pages assumed)

